{"tid":2431030,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朴春6個月減11kg「魔鬼食譜曝光」　主持人見狀倒抽一口氣","createTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T11:02:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb09aa7ea81fafa66e19a46666055fa2f131800","tid":2431030,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"南韓女歌手朴春出身自女團「2NE1」，曾經是KPOP的代表團體之一，2020年6月出席南韓大鐘獎電影節紅毯，卻因爆肥的身型引發討論，她日前透過減肥診所的幫助在半年內鏟肉11公斤，目前都是維持同樣的體重，減肥秘訣也因此備受關注，對此，她近日登上真人秀《On&amp;Off》曝光飲食管理的秘訣，光是早餐就令人驚呼「吃得飽嗎」，對於飲食控管非常嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5482/d5482064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5482%2Fd5482064.jpg&h=b4e5d596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼朴春減肥食譜曝光，量少到主持人倒抽一口氣。（圖／翻攝自Diggle Youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5482/d5482062.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5482%2Fd5482062.jpg&h=728adc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朴春近日出演真人秀《On&amp;Off》，同時公開自己的減肥秘訣，就是必須吃到3餐，且每天維持在同個時間吃飯，分別為早餐8點、中餐12點以及晚餐5點，為提醒自己準時吃飯，她特地在每個時刻設了鬧鐘，就連每餐的量都固定，透過節目公開的早餐食譜，她早上只吃5個玄米小飯糰以及生菜苤藍、萵苣，看起來份量極少，連主持人都倒抽一口氣懷疑「能吃飽嗎」，但她表示「還是會有飽足感」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5482/d5482060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5482%2Fd5482060.jpg&h=30afdb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴春靠著飲食控管成功瘦身11kg。（圖／翻攝自朴春IG）<br />\n<br />\n為了減肥，朴春已經戒了6個月麵包，拍攝當天，她忍不住誘惑吃了一口麵包，當被經紀人發現時，她立刻露出心虛的表情，但經紀人只回「姐姐幸福就好了」，她與經紀人間的互動也成了另一個關注焦點，粉絲直指兩人的情誼很溫暖。"},{"pid":"db7b5c7a72590904900ef79b0e87795e4faf32cf","tid":2431030,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"支持...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e64a85e81b38e4295902a0d0deb714de06493","tid":2431030,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7b5c7a72590904900ef79b0e87795e4faf32cf","tid":2431030,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"支持...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:53:09.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ffb208e8e5d3125ad60962b68cdd3cf71fd945","tid":2431030,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309f24c5f33b28a2d8d3ed8c2aa3cd4b1da1b670","tid":2431030,"uid":41509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"止唔止11k 啊?<br />\n睇個兩張圖,起碼差20k 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231082be3edb67e7bf8bcea50d31f91d41024ffd","tid":2431030,"uid":7050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"佢好樣衰，整容整到痴線"},{"pid":"324c4545af58b6baf0350505aab88ba251e81183","tid":2431030,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"整容塊面都肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d707a30d1c86b9de88c7d37f26958dfe7b84546b","tid":2431030,"uid":17513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbcUx3S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbcUx3S.gif&h=757820af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6個月先減11kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}